title: Hello super bugs and Dr. V's Top 7
description:
Antibiotics are being funnelled into our food system and that is causing big problems for us.  Say hello to super bugs.

Jillian is joined by Dr. Katja Van Herle (board certified UCLA endocrinologist).  This week it's "The Top 7 Reasons You Need Sleep."  This one will blow your mind. Jillian takes caller questions on diet, fitness, nutrition, inspiration and overall wellness.
